<subSubSection pageId="15" pageNumber="141" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="15.[1976,2628,886,1312]" pageId="15" pageNumber="141">
Has been sometimes considered to include 
<taxonomicName box="[2131,2238,1005,1038]" class="Mammalia" family="Felidae" genus="Felis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Carnivora" pageId="15" pageNumber="141" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="badia">C. badia</taxonomicName>
as a subspecies, but genetic analysis shows that the two are better considered separate species. Three subspecies recognized.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
